'''兩湖秋收暴動'''，又稱'''秋收動亂'''、'''秋收起事'''、'''秋收暴動'''，是1927年9月[[中国共产党|中国共产党]]按《中央關於湘鄂粵贛四省農民秋收暴動大綱》<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-hans | publisher = 中国共产党新闻_党的历史文献集和当代文献集_中共中央文件选集三（1927） | title = "中央关于湘鄂粤赣四省农民秋收暴动大纲" | url = http://cpc.people.com.cn/GB/64184/64186/66630/4489473.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140203100302/http://cpc.people.com.cn/GB/64184/64186/66630/4489473.html | archivedate = 2014-02-03 | access-date = 2014-01-23 | dead-url = no }}</ref>所規劃的一連串的暴動，是一個涉及四省的全盤暴動計畫。[[毛澤東|毛澤東]]並未參與決策，僅領導[[湖南|湖南]]、[[江西|江西]]邊界的湘南一路，此外湖南還有湘東（中）、湘西兩路。至於[[湖北|湖北]]，則計畫有七處暴動。

據統計，當時中共在中國各地發動了大小100多次武裝暴動，遍及14省140餘縣（市）。規模和影響較大的有湖北鄂中、鄂西特委於1927年9月領導的沔陽、監利、公安等縣的暴動；1927年10月有[[馮平|馮平]]領導的海南島暴動、[[楊靖宇|馬尚德]]（楊靖宇）領導的河南[[確山暴動|確山暴動]]、[[唐澍|唐澍]]等領導的陝西[[清澗暴動|清澗暴動]]；1927年11月有[[吳光浩|吳光浩]]領導的湖北[[黃麻暴動|黃麻暴動]]、[[曾天宇|曾天宇]]領導的江西東固等地的[[万安暴动|万安暴动]]；1927年12月[[張太雷|張太雷]]等領導的[[广州起义_(1927年)|廣州暴動]]。秋收暴動延伸到1928年還有[[方志敏|方志敏]]等領導的江西[[弋橫暴動|弋橫暴動]]；[[朱德|朱德]]、[[陳毅|陳毅]]領導的[[湘南暴動|湘南暴動]]；[[賀龍|賀龍]]、周逸群領導的湖南桑植暴動；朱積壘等領導的閩西暴動，[[劉志丹|劉志丹]]、唐澍等領導的陝西渭華暴動；[[彭德懷|彭德懷]]等領導的湖南[[平江暴動|平江暴動]]。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.sina.com.cn/c/sd/2011-07-14/103522812693.shtml|title=方志敏：两条半枪闹革命_新闻中心_新浪网|accessdate=2016-09-26|work=news.sina.com.cn|archive-date=2021-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210507131043/http://news.sina.com.cn/c/sd/2011-07-14/103522812693.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 经过 ==
1927年[[蔣中正|蔣中正]]的[[武漢國民政府|武漢國民政府]]和[[汪精衛|汪精衛]]的[[汪精衛政權|南京國民政府]]先後[[中国国民党清党|清黨]]之後，[[史達林|史達林]]派[[羅明納茲|羅明納茲]]至[[漢口|漢口]]召開[[八七會議|八七會議]]，確定此後以[[瞿秋白|瞿秋白]]主持[[中共中央|中共中央]]領導工作<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://view.news.qq.com/a/20130531/003478.htm|title=七大前实际主持中央工作的领导人是谁|accessdate=2016-09-26|author=|date=|work=view.news.qq.com|publisher=腾讯网|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417065114/https://view.news.qq.com/a/20130531/003478.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這次會議決定了[[中國共產黨|中共]]今後的總方針：[[土地革命|土地革命]]和武裝反抗[[中國國民黨|中國國民黨]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://dangshi.people.com.cn/GB/165617/166496/168108/10011255.html|title=八七会议(1927年8月7日)--中国共产党新闻--人民网|accessdate=2016-09-26|work=dangshi.people.com.cn|archive-date=2012-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121225130943/http://dangshi.people.com.cn/GB/165617/166496/168108/10011255.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
[[File:Site_of_Joining_Forces_in_Wenjiashi_of_Autumn_Harvest_Uprising_008.jpg|缩略图]]]]
八七會後，[[毛泽东|毛泽东]]以[[中共中央|中共中央]]特派员和[[中共中央政治局|中共中央政治局]]候补委员的身份<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://cpc.people.com.cn/GB/75289/6221169.html|title=“霹雳一声暴动”——纪念秋收起义80周年--中国共产党新闻--中国共产党新闻网|accessdate=2016-09-26|work=cpc.people.com.cn|archive-date=2017-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305001653/http://cpc.people.com.cn/GB/75289/6221169.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Uv6eCwAAQBAJ&pg=PA67&dq=%25E6%25AF%259B%25E6%25B3%25BD%25E4%25B8%259C%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%2591%2598%25E5%2592%258C%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%2580%2599%25E8%25A1%25A5%25E5%25A7%2594%25E5%2591%2598%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BB%25BD%25EF%25BC%258C&hl=zh-CN&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwit0qmuoK3PAhXBwj4KHe8jCokQ6AEIJTAB#v=onepage&q&f=false|title=CHINESE COMMUNIST PARTY AND MODERN CHINESE POLITICS|last=YANG|first=ZHENGLIAN|date=2016-02-23|publisher=American Academic Press|isbn=9781631817724|language=zh|access-date=2016-09-26|archive-date=2021-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210507131101/https://books.google.com/books?id=Uv6eCwAAQBAJ&pg=PA67&dq=%25E6%25AF%259B%25E6%25B3%25BD%25E4%25B8%259C%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%2591%2598%25E5%2592%258C%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%2580%2599%25E8%25A1%25A5%25E5%25A7%2594%25E5%2591%2598%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BB%25BD%25EF%25BC%258C&hl=zh-CN&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwit0qmuoK3PAhXBwj4KHe8jCokQ6AEIJTAB#v=onepage&q&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>，于1927年8月18日携夫人[[杨开慧|杨开慧]]及其儿子抵达[[长沙|长沙]]，参加了改组[[中共湖南省委|中共湖南省委]]会议<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://cpc.people.com.cn/GB/64162/64165/70293/70302/4796026.html|title=1927年9月9日 秋收起义--中国共产党新闻--中国共产党新闻网|accessdate=2016-09-26|work=cpc.people.com.cn|archive-date=2017-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305001614/http://cpc.people.com.cn/GB/64162/64165/70293/70302/4796026.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[湖南省|湖南省]]委書記[[彭公达|彭公达]]和[[毛澤東|毛澤東]]前往[[湖南省|湖南]]組織秋收暴動。8月30日，[[湖南省|湖南省]]委开会决定缩小暴动区域<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://cpc.people.com.cn/GB/75289/6221190.html|title=关于毛泽东同志领导秋收起义时的身份问题--中国共产党新闻--中国共产党新闻网|accessdate=2016-09-26|work=cpc.people.com.cn|archive-date=2017-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170903032145/http://cpc.people.com.cn/GB/75289/6221190.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以[[长沙|长沙]]为中心，决定成立以[[毛泽东|毛泽东]]为书记的[[中国共产党|中国共产党]]前敌委员会<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=RSc7CwAAQBAJ&pg=PT518&lpg=PT518&dq=%25E5%2586%25B3%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25AB%258B%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%25AF%259B%25E6%25B3%25BD%25E4%25B8%259C%25E4%25B8%25BA%25E4%25B9%25A6%25E8%25AE%25B0%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%2589%258D%25E6%2595%258C%25E5%25A7%2594%25E5%2591%2598%25E4%25BC%259A&source=bl&ots=EewQloAG-m&sig=rMrWvo8rbHSkTKLbpsl5M2_XQuw&hl=zh-CN&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiC5s_JoK3PAhXDNT4KHXGHC64Q6AEIKzAC#v=onepage&q&f=false|title=毛泽东和他的父老乡亲（上下册）|last=赵志超|date=2015-12-19|publisher=湖南文艺出版社; Esphere Media（美国艾思传媒）|isbn=9787540450748|language=zh|access-date=2016-09-26|archive-date=2021-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210507132544/https://books.google.com/books?id=RSc7CwAAQBAJ&pg=PT518&lpg=PT518&dq=%25E5%2586%25B3%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25AB%258B%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%25AF%259B%25E6%25B3%25BD%25E4%25B8%259C%25E4%25B8%25BA%25E4%25B9%25A6%25E8%25AE%25B0%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%2589%258D%25E6%2595%258C%25E5%25A7%2594%25E5%2591%2598%25E4%25BC%259A&source=bl&ots=EewQloAG-m&sig=rMrWvo8rbHSkTKLbpsl5M2_XQuw&hl=zh-CN&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiC5s_JoK3PAhXDNT4KHXGHC64Q6AEIKzAC#v=onepage&q&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>，发动湘赣边界秋收暴动<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=8R04AQAAIAAJ&q=8%25E6%259C%258830%25E6%2597%25A5%25EF%25BC%258C%25E6%25B9%2596%25E5%258D%2